  "description": [
    "rFie Milwaukee Leader What Are Republicans For It is out of order to register surprise because of the testimony that Claudius Houston chairman of the Republican national com mittee essayed to assist in drafting Muscle Shoals planks in both the Republican and the Democratic national platform of 1928 So also there was no occasion for astonishment when it was revealed that he had been engaged in an effort to secure the Muscle Shoals plant for the American Cyanamid Company previous to his elevation to the chairmanship of the Republican party Nor is it surprising that Hoover did not demand Houstons resignation as chairman of the party when it became known that the latter had been representing the Cyanamid Company It is an extremely undesirable condition of things of course but it is what is to be expected of the Republican party and of Re publican politicians The Republican party like the Democratic party is a political representative of the parasitic elements of society Some of those elements are bent upon securing control of Muscle Shoals and the other power sites It is most natural that the Republican party and its chairman should give them aid and comfort What are Repub"
  ],
